Things to do at Quail Run
During Snowbird season November through April we have various activities that everyone is welcome
           to participate in. This list is just a sample of some of the things that are happening at Quail Run.
           If you are interested in our full lineup of events you can download our current calendar from the links
           at the bottom of the page.
These are some of our regularly scheduled weekly recurring events. 
           Every night there are card games being played in the Quails Nest.
For exact time of these events please see the monthly calendar link below.

Must be a registered guest and 18 years old to play Bingo.
In addition to the above activities we will also have other scheduled activities.
Here are
           a few of the other non weekly activities that we will have:
1. Live Entertainment. $$
2. Party or Dinner for most Holidays.
3. Themed  Dances. $$
4. New Years Eve Party. $$
5. Kentucky Derby Night.
6. Casino Night.
7. Classic Car Show. (March)
8. Other activities as suggested by residents and visitors of Quail Run.
If you would like a full calendar of events you may download a copy of our
Current Month Calendar
or a copy of the
Prior Month Calendar
